    <item>
      <title>摩根大通放弃在美国大选前购买中国股票的建议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/jpmorgan-abandons-bullish-china-call-as-us-election-stirs-angst</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通放弃了对中国股票的买入建议，理由是即将到来的美国大选将加剧中国股票的波动，此外还面临着经济增长阻力和政策支持不力等因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/jpmorgan-abandons-bullish-china-call-as-us-election-stirs-angst</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 22:13:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标准普尔警告称，负债累累的新西兰地方议会面临评级下调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/debt-burdened-new-zealand-councils-face-downgrades-s-p-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级表示，新西兰一些地方议会的债务水平在全球同行中名列前茅，信用评级下调可能是不可避免的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/debt-burdened-new-zealand-councils-face-downgrades-s-p-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 21:49:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管分歧加剧，习近平的影响力仍吸引非洲精英来到北京</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/xi-s-clout-draws-african-elite-to-beijing-even-as-fissures-grow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于债务批评和中国经济放缓限制了北京通过贷款建立影响力的能力，国家主席习近平将制定发展中国与非洲关系的蓝图。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/xi-s-clout-draws-african-elite-to-beijing-even-as-fissures-grow</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
