      <title>特朗普竞选团队 8 月份支出比筹集的资金多 3200 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/trump-campaign-spent-32-million-more-than-it-raised-in-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着总统竞选进入迄今为止最激烈、最昂贵的阶段，唐纳德·特朗普动用了自己的竞选资金，试图阻止民主党对手卡马拉·哈里斯的势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/trump-campaign-spent-32-million-more-than-it-raised-in-august</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 20:12:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 筹款闪电战由加密货币支持者发起</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/kamala-harris-fundraising-blitz-in-works-by-supporters-in-crypto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的加密行业支持者正在努力在未来几周内建立至少八次筹款活动，以造福民主党候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/kamala-harris-fundraising-blitz-in-works-by-supporters-in-crypto</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 20:08:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡寻求以色列控制加沙食品分配</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/netanyahu-calls-for-israeli-control-over-gaza-food-distribution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡周三表示，以色列计划从哈马斯手中夺取对加沙地带粮食分配的控制权，他称此举是为了阻止哈马斯霸占人道主义援助物资的做法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/netanyahu-calls-for-israeli-control-over-gaza-food-distribution</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 18:48:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将阻止新日铁收购美国钢铁公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/biden-to-block-nippon-steel-us-steel-deal-washington-post-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国总统拜登正准备阻止新日本制铁公司以 141 亿美元收购美国钢铁公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/biden-to-block-nippon-steel-us-steel-deal-washington-post-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 17:59:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普减税的成本将超过几乎所有联邦机构的成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/trump-tax-cuts-would-cost-more-than-almost-all-federal-agencies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 和竞选搭档 JD 万斯 (JD Vance) 正在竞选中提出一系列减税方案，这些方案在未来十年的总成本可能高达 10.5 万亿美元，这一巨额金额将超过国内所有联邦机构的预算总和。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/trump-tax-cuts-would-cost-more-than-almost-all-federal-agencies</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 14:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
